{"tid":527015,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[jj插沙]跪求解答做中文老師既問題","createTime":"2018-01-12T08:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T17:42:38.000Z","uid":36334,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6edd30f721eb9eee7dadd2df23a214e16d3956","tid":527015,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想問下關於做老師既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細佬我讀緊中大中文系，想第日讀pgde然後做老師。<br />\n<br />\n但依加就有d煩惱緊min history既問題，究竟min科對入pgde/第日做老師搵工有冇關係？低form係咪點都教得？而高form一定要major in history先教得？<br />\n<br />\n另外，pgde係睇gpa重d，定教學經驗，或者有min科咁？<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290f33d7b4e170da5afd4f90af24b63ace7846f7","tid":527015,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"推一推，維民所止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d170edfc5e95a67bd9c029a2eb4d57af0ff6f7","tid":527015,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58479c67352502b084d79936fa353a68127abd10","tid":527015,"uid":36334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113ae54ac9a3f6232f5b294734239ae733af39c9","tid":527015,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a7f4d20124f